author: Austin Evans
description:
Thank you to Creative Electron for the X-Ray images! https://creativeelectron.com/

Just got my hands on Sony's brand new PS5 Slim 2100 revision and what I found inside is honestly baffling. They've somehow made the console lighter and more efficient but then made one decision that's going to make you question everything. Is this really what we're paying €500 for in 2025?
